snippet.title: How Age and Genetics will Affect Your Cycling Performance (Ask a Cycling Coach 255)
snippet.description:
Why starting cycling later in life won't ruin your cycling performance potential, how to know if you are genetically gifted for endurance sports, plus how to find your strengths and boost performance regardless of your genetics and more all in this Quick Clip from Episode 255 of The Ask a Cycling Coach Podcast.

• Find links to mentioned studies and join the discussion on the TrainerRoad Forum: https://bit.ly/34QVk6u

• Watch more of this episode: https://youtu.be/htDYWoZBVw0
